{"tid":1131430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真相越辯越明 話今次反杜汶澤係五毛老屈果班不如收收皮","createTime":"2019-04-29T15:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T17:14:14.000Z","uid":171273,"like":28,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ce4629cb49c47265d5a3ab75834a476bdf783d","tid":1131430,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"咩五毛造文章<br />\n<br />\n咩分散注意力等人唔去遊行<br />\n<br />\n咩遊行完左無人再講<br />\n<br />\n不如班乜柒都陰謀論既撚樣收撚皮啦<br />\n<br />\n人地有證有據 有圖有片<br />\n<br />\n件事會搞大原因就係杜汶澤最初公開指摘程美段<br />\n<br />\n連登第一個post都係幸災樂禍話終於屌柒車厘龜<br />\n<br />\n後來女方不斷放出證據 先一直有人討論<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解會比班乜都屈毛既鍵國憤青話分散注意力<br />\n<br />\n討論所有只要唔係主力反共既新聞討論下都比你班撚樣屈毛<br />\n<br />\n個個post入黎單單打打 又咩戰狼又盛 都痴撚柒線"},{"pid":"7718efcfb99f2a641efb9eda775bf45aa426d655","tid":1131430,"uid":79563,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"條仆街杜汶澤無賴到話「無講過何時出糧」<br />\n程美段公開咗錄音<br />\n原來係應承咗一個星期出<br />\n點知要人地追到千山萬水<br />\n<br />\n我發覺凡追捧黃毓民既人<br />\n都有唔同程度既柒"},{"pid":"e96241fd1e39166691b1f3676e3dd388403efda5","tid":1131430,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/XJDNMVN1/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FXJDNMVN1%2Fimage.jpg&h=d6b50765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcab80caabd04b221e3aabd01b4731a2362de0d","tid":1131430,"uid":171273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e96241fd1e39166691b1f3676e3dd388403efda5","tid":1131430,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/XJDNMVN1/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FXJDNMVN1%2Fimage.jpg&h=d6b50765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/