 />\n唔撚推紅佢<br />\n致於unlike行動<br />\n難聽啲講 連登有幾多人？<br />\n收皮啦 對佢係影響<br />\n除非佢真係衰好大獲<br />\n到時唔需要你班連登仔<br />\n佢都會收皮"},{"pid":"6d1347f652a991b363f9b09a630eb46632540d5e","tid":1131430,"uid":124372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:41:59.000Z","msg":"我堂堂本土你話我鳩五毛<br />\n我宜家正式屌你杜汶澤老母+冚家剷<br />\n唔好同我講一人做事一人當<br />\n一人做事係要死全家的<br />\n我屌你老婆"},{"pid":"4c64f9a1ae48d69695da14ee493fb18b40a2cee1","tid":1131430,"uid":193092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d1347f652a991b363f9b09a630eb46632540d5e","tid":1131430,"uid":124372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:41:59.000Z","msg":"我堂堂本土你話我鳩五毛<br />\n我宜家正式屌你杜汶澤老母+冚家剷<br />\n唔好同我講一人做事一人當<br />\n一人做事係要死全家的<br />\n我屌你老婆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:32:59.000Z","msg":"呀田都屌？"},{"pid":"eb5eb746fecc931da7ee0965f297eff372cf2064","tid":1131430,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:39:55.000Z","msg":"五毛無老屈，但五毛會盡全力開火"},{"pid":"a3e75c005e06c9423f51fba88e3edd00065069d6","tid":1131430,"uid":217450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:41:35.000Z","msg":"咁都撐杜狗嗰啲係幾垃圾"},{"pid":"ec1947301dbc23be656eacd2189394d9d3d04305","tid":1131430,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb5eb746fecc931da7ee0965f297eff372cf2064","tid":1131430,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T20:39:55.000Z","msg":"五毛無老屈，但五毛會盡全力開火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T21:29:48.000Z","msg":"老實講 自己畀曬位人入 怪得邊個<br />\n自己唔柒碌都唔會全城圍插啦<br />\n唔講賓穎講句反共 就代表佢搞人老公唔屌得咩<br />\n杜怯要怪就怪自己冇人格啦"},{"pid":"97ac37ba7f4575ce34c6fc535aa2b2714267bfaf","tid":1131430,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb1b29fc8637591fc012ddf72c3d22812acff4ec","tid":1131430,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23efcebad87bd4c66bd118358c030edc0dab978b","tid":1131430,"uid":75782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:00:02.